Closely related to the bulk flow is the Local Group peculiar velocity inferred from the observed CMB dipole [483] 1.7.41\documentclass[12pt]{minimal}
				\usepackage{amsmath}
				\usepackage{wasysym}
				\usepackage{amsfonts}
				\usepackage{amssymb}
				\usepackage{amsbsy}
				\usepackage{mathrsfs}
