				\usepackage{mathrsfs}
				\usepackage{upgreek}
				\setlength{\oddsidemargin}{-69pt}
				\begin{document}${\xi _V} \equiv M_{{\rm{Pl}}}^4{{{V\prime}{V^{\prime\prime\prime}}} \over {{V^2}}}$\end{document}.

The spectrum of tensor fluctuations is given by 3.2.11\documentclass[12pt]{minimal}
				\usepackage{amsmath}
				\usepackage{wasysym}
				\usepackage{amsfonts}
